Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:48.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\yshad3}拉開帷幕的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:53.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\yshad3}讓人感到心潮澎湃
